data.description: Well maintained home in Kalkaska Township is affordable and move in ready! This home boast 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, a jetted tub, laminate flooring and a pellet stove that keeps heating cost low.  There is also a detached heated garage and garden/storage shed.  The back yard is fenced for your pets, and the lot is nearly an acre in size. Beautiful gardens adorn the outside of the home in the summer, when you can enjoy a covered porch out front or a very private deck out back.
